summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Home & Own Real Estate Platform. Backend authentication and property creation working, but frontend React app not rendering and several backend endpoints have issues.

critical_bugs.issue: User profile access failing despite successful login - JWT token authentication not working properly for profile endpoints
critical_bugs.impact: Users cannot access their profile information after login

critical_bugs.issue: Returns 404 Not Found when submitting property inquiries
critical_bugs.impact: Users cannot submit inquiries for properties - core functionality broken

critical_bugs.issue: Returns 404 Not Found when submitting tour bookings
critical_bugs.impact: Users cannot book property tours - core functionality broken

flaky_endpoints.symptoms: Admin endpoints returning empty data despite successful authentication
flaky_endpoints.workaround: Check admin token authentication and database connectivity

critical_bugs.issue: React application not rendering - blank page with no content
critical_bugs.impact: Complete frontend failure - users cannot access any functionality

critical_bugs.issue: Login form not rendering - no input fields or buttons visible
critical_bugs.impact: Users cannot log in to the system

integration_issues.issue: Frontend may not be connecting to backend properly due to environment variable issues
integration_issues.details: VITE_PY_API_URL environment variable not set, defaulting to production URL

passed_tests: Authentication endpoints for all user types (admin, buyer, seller, agent)
Role-based access control - buyers/sellers correctly blocked from admin endpoints
Property creation with partial data (not all fields required)
Backend server connectivity and basic API responses
action_item_for_main_agent: CRITICAL: Frontend React app is not rendering at all - investigate JavaScript errors, environment variables (VITE_PY_API_URL), and build issues. Backend inquiry/booking endpoints returning 404 - check routing configuration. JWT token authentication for profile access needs fixing.

success_percentage.backend: 50% - Authentication working, property CRUD working, but inquiry/booking/admin endpoints failing
success_percentage.frontend: 0% - Complete failure, React app not rendering
